"{\"uid\": \"ign.com-articles-tom-cruise-olympics-stunt-sees-top-gun-star-pass-the-torch-by-diving-into-a-crowd-of-olympians\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruise made a special appearance at the 2024 Paris Olympics closing ceremony to perform an electrifying stunt.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The feat saw the action movie star leap from the top of the Stade de France and into a crowd of Olympians.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After being greeted by the world's greatest athletes, gymnast Simone Biles handed him the flag so it could be transported to the home of the 2028 Olympic Games: Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 5.186587125582241e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise then took off on his motorcycle, flag in tow, leading to a pre-recorded segment where he drives through Paris and jumps out of a plane before ending his globe-trotting journey at the Hollywood sign in California.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.381889370150851e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999807160267584, \"rank\": 1.9280783956975425e-05, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impossible n'est pas Tom Cruise qui descend au milieu du Stade de France !#Paris2024#ceremoniedecloturepic.twitter.com/XL1i4ffM16  It was a moment straight out of a Mission Impossible movie.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Artist H.E.R.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.231456197584312e-30, \"text\": \"H.E.R.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"even helped channel the action movie vibes by playing Cruise in with music from the film.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise's Olympics closing ceremony stunt became one of the most anticipated events of the Olympics afterreports indicated he would be involved in the showa few weeks ago.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Few details about what the stunt would be were shared at the time, so it's no surprise to see the actor show up with something truly mind-boggling today.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Top Gun star wasn't the only celebrity to help pass the torch to the forthcoming 2028 Los Angeles Olympics.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"California-based artists Billie Eilish, Red Hot Chili Peppers, and Snoop Dogg also put on performances to help welcome the world ahead of the next summer games.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billie_Eilish\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Billie Eilish\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billie_Eilish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billie_Eilish\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Hot Chili Peppers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}, {\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you, Paris!\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now off to LA.pic.twitter.com/MxlAb0hZbT  The 2024 Paris Olympic Games have come to a close, but they left us with highlights that we will enjoy for years to come.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of our favorite moments saw the internet gathering to drawanime-inspired fan